PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION (a) to sell some 17.25 hectares of vacant land situated on the northwest corner of Woodroffe Ave. and Fallowfield Road, in the City of Nepean, to the REGION OF OTTAWA- CARLETON, and (b) to grant an EASEMENT to the Region across a strip of land on the opposite (east) side of Woodroffe and eastwardly along the railway right-of-way, for the installation of a storm water sewer pipe.
